it.uniud.mads.jlibbig.core

Interface Matcher<A extends Bigraph<?>,R extends Bigraph<?>>

  • Type Parameters:
    A - kind of the 'agent' bigraph.
    R - kind of the redex.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AgentMatcher, Matcher, WeightedMatcher

    public interface Matcher<A extends Bigraph<?>,R extends Bigraph<?>>
    Provides services for computing the matches of a bigraph (sometimes called redex) into an other. In particular, a match of a bigraph R in G is a triple yielding G when composed. The bigraphs C, R, and P are called Context, Redex and Prameter of the match respectively. Matches are described by implementations of Match.
